body:
@tanishqjasoria I think we should modify and change IfPoolIsNotEmpty to more of if TxSource is returning transactions? We would not build empty blocks then.

We could also add TxPool configuration value, should we allow transactions under basefee to be included (some people want this feature, some people don't). You can contact @marcindsobczak we should have some code in history ready to be used, just parametrized.

Last but not least, can we make initial basefee of genesis somehow configurable?
